<item>
            <title>[NIFI-3607] TailFile does not notice new files in folder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NIFI-3607</link>
                <project id="12316020" key="NIFI">Apache NiFi</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have configured the TailFile processor to read multiple (small) files from a folder.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This works, but if more files are created in the folder, the processor does not pick them up, even though the &quot;Lookup frequency&quot; is set (10 minutes).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I stop and start the processor, it correctly picks up the new files.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
